### 1. Create knowledge source
POST http://localhost:8000/api/knowledge-sources
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workspace_id": "demo-workspace",
  "name": "本地示例健康资讯",
  "source_type": "website",
  "url": "http://127.0.0.1:8000/demo/sample_health_news.html",
  "crawl_frequency": "daily",
  "category": "睡眠健康",
  "credibility_level": "medium"
}

### 2. Crawl knowledge source
POST http://localhost:8000/api/knowledge-sources/{{source_id}}/crawl

### 3. List knowledge items
GET http://localhost:8000/api/knowledge-items?source_id={{source_id}}

